ks with your layout:</strong> In small rooms, avoid rugs that take up too much floor space. In larger bedrooms, a bigger rug under the bed creates a balanced, cozy look.<br><br><strong>•  Think about comfort and care: </strong>Go for rugs that feel good underfoot and are <a href="https://www.lanyspace.com/blogs/rug-inspirations-and-trends/lany-space-rug-care-guide-how-to-clean-and-care-for-your-polyester-rug-the-easy-way" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(1, 126, 86);"><u>easy to clean</u></span></a>. Low-pile or washable options work especially well in bedrooms.<br><br><strong>•  Stick to what fits your budget:</strong> Focus on size and placement first. Once that's right, you'll find plenty of styles to choose from within your price range.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-39_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-40_"><img title="Soft, cozy rug" alt="Soft, cozy rug" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0619/2998/0042/files/10-2.webp?v=1749693735&width=1920 1920w,https:/